Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.17,0:03:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta hang in there!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.93,0:03:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't drive like a madman! {?? don't really here what driving}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.73,0:03:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,God! Buddha! Or even the Devil! {? unsure, maybe it's ryota who she calls devil}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.58,0:03:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I get off earlier?! {??????}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there! You can do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.34,0:03:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting! The baby's coming! {assuming this achau is akachan}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.93,0:03:42.61,Top,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.61,0:03:46.60,Top,,0,0,0,,I'll take you straight to the hospital!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.30,0:03:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Everyone on board, we'll hit a rough patch up ahead, so hang on to your seats, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.38,0:04:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramps and grannies with dentures, \Nhold your mouths shut.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.98,0:04:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go! Make way for Lord Rolling Ryota! {-sama}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.06,0:04:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Hurry it up! It's coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.46,0:04:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm gonna pee my pants!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.08,0:04:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch. Why stop now of all times?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.32,0:04:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When someone's in trouble, you help.\N That's what you do.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.56,0:04:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did that?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.73,0:04:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Upsy-daisy...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.02,0:04:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that old hag?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.82,0:04:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Old women these days \Nare more spoiled than kids.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.99,0:04:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.40,0:05:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get off quickly, will you?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time I'm taking away the priority seats. {senior citizen; pensioner seats - probably means he'll physically remove them from the bus}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeoff!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.82,0:05:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.31,0:05:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn to understand other people's pain, \Nfrom your own experience.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.80,0:05:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.27,0:05:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.25,0:05:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! There were tons of people \Nwaiting at that stop.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.44,0:06:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it okay to blow right past it?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.11,0:06:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an express to the hospital!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.31,0:06:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, our bus...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.44,0:06:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.77,0:06:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop the bus! I want to get off here!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.82,0:06:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're taking off. {lit: going to fly}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.97,0:06:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.61,0:06:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're flying!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.99,0:06:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A cliff?! {?????????? actually no clue, could be anything}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.05,0:06:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it! Three hours, one minute, \Nthirty-two seconds. A new record!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.27,0:06:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mama-to-be! We've arrived. {??????? nc what's that rajimama}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.29,0:06:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He was trying to kill us! {????? actually "being killed" in future/present tense but idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.39,0:07:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A penny a day. \NDid a good deed today too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.78,0:07:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.48,0:07:09.28,Top,,0,0,0,,Takao-kun, you've done it again!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.28,0:07:12.87,Top,,0,0,0,,You're the biggest threat to public safety \Nthis town has ever seen!{lit: All you ever do is cause trouble for antisotta! - no clue what it could be, but "an" could mean "safe" so it's probably something about public safety}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.42,0:07:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Driving a bus like a madman, not stopping\N at bus stops... What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.66,0:07:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Complaints are flooding in!\N What are we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.16,0:07:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you cause trouble again, you'll be...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.75,0:07:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, I understand!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be careful. Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.18,0:07:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And one more thing: no checking racing tips in the driver's seat. Got it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.85,0:07:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch. I already have to refrain \Nfrom betting at my workplace,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and now I can't even make predictions? Fuck me... {??? something about predictions, probably means "can't even consider what to bet on thanks to reading tips”}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.79,0:07:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, your job's on the line too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.12,0:07:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God. Thank God!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You did really well.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.38,0:08:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also thanks to that bus driver.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.40,0:08:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My shoulders are killing me today.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.12,0:08:18.83,Top,,0,0,0,,You pissed off the manager again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.54,0:08:24.19,Top,,0,0,0,,If you keep acting like a total moron, \Nyou'll get fired, Ryo-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.96,0:08:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All the bikers around the country\N are scared stiff. Rolling Ryota...{I'm confident that the word is prevalent enough outside japan, since even my non-anime friend used it once; otherwise, maybe "biker gangs"}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.26,0:08:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's settling down as a bus driver?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.62,0:08:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No way he'd be able to stand it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.85,0:08:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi, you've had enough for tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.36,0:08:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What, already? It's still early.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ryo-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.65,0:08:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask. Just go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.19,0:08:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. If that's the case, I'll make myself scarce. \NMika, how much is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.72,0:08:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,On me tonight. Ryo-chan's treat.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.58,0:08:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! That'd be rude to my boss! {lit: rude to aniki }
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.77,0:08:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be shy.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.46,0:09:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange, make sure my car\N gets fixed up real good.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.38,0:09:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's what you meant?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.83,0:09:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure. Consider it done.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.81,0:09:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo-chan, I love you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.34,0:09:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.17,0:09:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, attaway.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.58,0:09:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.57,0:09:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Spare me! Spare me! {/sorry}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.54,0:12:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunday shift, pathetic...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.74,0:12:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch. I'm out of luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.52,0:12:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!{Ush!}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.01,0:12:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No wins at pachinko,\N no girls to hang out with.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.60,0:12:59.07,Top,,0,0,0,,What rotten luck, just as we finally have\N a Sunday all to ourselves. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why's there a bus here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.39,0:13:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This narrow backstreet's\N no place for a bus!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.31,0:13:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Watch out!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.28,0:13:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, bussing motherfucker!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.19,0:13:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.99,0:13:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.91,0:13:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you dimwits throw that stone?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.29,0:13:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa there! For a bus driver, you're pretty flashy. {referring to his bosozoku hairstyle}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.63,0:13:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked if you threw it or not!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.98,0:13:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you picking a fight with us members\N of the Panthers biker gang?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.80,0:13:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Toshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.60,0:13:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You prick!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.57,0:13:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of hanging around \Nlike you've got nothing better to do,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,think of the folks stuck working the Sunday shift.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.47,0:14:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.37,0:14:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.83,0:14:12.71,Top,,0,0,0,,That's got to be Rolling Ryota.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.31,0:14:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rolling Ryota?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.58,0:14:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not another bus driver\Nin the world as reckless as him. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.53,0:14:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who {\i1}is{\i0} that guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.64,0:14:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's from another era, \Nso of course you wouldn't know him. {probably means older generation of bosozoku, as in one who moved on and retired/settled down before they joined the gang}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.05,0:14:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we don't know him, \Nbut if this keeps up...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.08,0:14:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I get wanting revenge...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.74,0:14:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but forget the wolf bite and move on. {idiom, meaning let bygones be bygones, a wolf bit you so what?}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.68,0:14:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.92,0:14:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are good-hearted \Nmembers of the Panthers.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.28,0:14:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to avoid dangerous people like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.87,0:14:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.12,0:14:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like this. \NEven Henmi-san's changed.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.68,0:14:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in the day, if the Panthers got hit, \Nwe wouldn't just be quiet.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.32,0:14:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.65,0:15:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd pick up our wooden swords \Nand raid the fuckers.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.56,0:15:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If the leader's like that, \Nthe Panthers won't last long.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.46,0:15:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.14,0:15:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But is Ryota really that dangerous?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.04,0:15:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? You can never tell from just one hit.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.11,0:15:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? \NYou were sprawled out back then. {lit: stretched - meaning he was lying on the ground unable to get up}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.24,0:15:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.50,0:15:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You were twitching too, weren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.42,0:15:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, he one-punch KO'd us both. \NThat's a hard fact, bro.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.54,0:15:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Toshi?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.49,0:15:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.77,0:15:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hang out with us, Ryo-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.77,0:15:39.67,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Ah... Hold up... Hey! I said no!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.67,0:15:43.88,Top,,0,0,0,,Working on a Sunday isn't like you, Ryo-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.34,Top,,0,0,0,,Hey, keep me company tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I said no, and that means no!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.02,0:15:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hang out with the likes of you, \NI'll end up losing something important!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.16,0:15:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't that Umeko, who you always fancied?\NAnd that guy with her...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.69,0:16:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo-chan, I feel so good. \NYou're reaching my deepest part! {??? I hear something about hitting so it's probably something around "that area is where it feels the best"}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.71,0:16:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, Umeko!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.57,0:16:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If I feel like it, I'll dump you! {???? dunno why but that seems to be what he's saying}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.94,0:16:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.84,0:16:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.27,0:16:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,To think "Ryo-chan" was him, of all guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.10,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you on about?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.21,0:16:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That Umeko always used to say,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.40,0:16:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ryo-chan's an idol. \NHe's too good for someone like me."
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just assumed...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.97,0:16:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Assumed what?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.46,0:16:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was Sugi Ryotaro! {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ry%C5%8Dtar%C5%8D_Sugi}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.76,0:16:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sugi Ryo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.76,0:16:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking? Surely, \Nshe wouldn't fall in love with someone that old!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.36,0:16:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But Umeko bought tickets \Nto Sugi Ryo's concert just the other day!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.86,0:16:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe her mom asked her to?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.46,0:17:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kawada! Tell me! {??? no clue what kawada is supposed to know about it}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.76,0:17:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about that!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.86,0:17:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Was Umeko actually in love with that guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.59,0:17:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! I was secretly practicing every night for her sake.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.52,0:17:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawada, that Ryota guy...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.06,0:17:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the bus depot is\N the best place to face him. {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.46,0:17:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Toshi, what are you...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch! Toshi, that idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.43,0:17:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cumming! I'm at my limit!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.38,0:17:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm getting there too!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.54,0:17:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi-san! Henmi-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.38,0:17:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch! Who's that, now of all times?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.90,0:17:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.74,0:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in trouble!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.00,0:17:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you again?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.42,0:17:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That punk Toshi got all fired up \Nand went to see Ryota on his own!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.62,0:18:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, what'll I do with that idiot?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.12,0:18:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's on him. I did warn you two, didn't I? {think he means "I don't care, it's his own fault" although could be "No telling what'll happen."}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.84,0:18:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Come with us, Henmi-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.45,0:18:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous! \NWhen Ryota's involved, you stay out of it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.37,0:18:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that! Please, Henmi-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.91,0:18:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Ryota really that tough?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.13,0:18:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Biker gangs from all over Japan \Nchallenged him, and nobody could touch him.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.80,0:18:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.83,0:18:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So give up, wontcha?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No way we will.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.48,0:18:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he's got a sworn \Nyounger brother he dotes on. {otoutobun again}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.26,0:18:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the leader of Sally Crown, \NTakashi, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.65,0:18:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we take that guy hostage?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.40,0:18:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's do that. \NThen Ryota won't be able to act.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.87,0:19:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A hostage, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.03,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's give it a shot.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.43,0:19:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takashi!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.51,0:19:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? B-Boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.82,0:19:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How's my car looking?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.93,0:19:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I'll have it done by evening.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.89,0:19:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a date tomorrow, \Nso make it perfect, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.71,0:19:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Go do your job.\NYou've got passengers waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.61,0:19:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.03,0:19:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just leave the car to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.78,0:19:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry! Get going!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.87,0:19:41.44,Overlap,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.44,0:19:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right, we're going.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then. {ja tanomu wa = alright, I entrust it to you then}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.54,0:19:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring it by tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.36,0:19:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's that worried, \Nhe's really fired up about tomorrow's girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.93,0:20:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that about a girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.52,0:20:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell! Yuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.08,0:20:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always wandering around.\N Do you even go to school?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.83,0:20:12.61,Top,,0,0,0,,I do! Twice a week.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.61,0:20:16.95,Top,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, you're still fixing \NRyota's car for free, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.95,0:20:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.52,0:20:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's silly. Just because Ryota helped you before, \Nyou're acting like his lackey.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.77,0:20:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you secretly like him? {lit: have that feeling - implying exactly what you think she implies}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.99,0:20:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, how pathetic.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.94,0:20:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I was thinking \Nthe leader of Sally Crown was my man... {??? idk why but she says "to think the leader of SC would be my man"}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.22,0:20:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who's your man?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.61,0:20:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't decide that for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.75,0:20:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! My stomach hurts! It hurts like\N I'm about to miscarry Taka-chan's baby! {?????? orosu = to abort (a fetus)​ but idk what she means; is she already pregnant? is she implying she can't get pregnant if he screams at her?}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.64,0:20:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.51,0:20:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it's fixed, I'll take you out, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.86,0:20:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that, but honestly, \Nyou couldn't be happier I came.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.88,0:21:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"It'll be free today."\NIsn't that what you truly think about?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're blushing! \NI hit the nail on the head!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.71,0:21:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez! Pervert! So you still \Ndon't have a woman to sleep with!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.65,0:21:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I shouldn't have to pay\N every time if it's with you! {??????}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.74,0:21:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.74,0:21:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, pathetic! \NRaping a girl at such a young age! {????????? lit: that youth, doing what you want with woman - no clue what she means, maybe that he's just mistreating her/not giving her what she wants; also that "youth" could be hers - "raping a girl that young!" but I don't care}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.16,0:21:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not that! {/you're wrong}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.90,0:21:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... That tickles!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.83,0:21:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Taka-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.72,0:21:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.67,0:21:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Taka-chan, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.22,0:21:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.39,0:21:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hide, Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.67,0:21:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it! Go hide now \Nif you don't wanna get gang-raped!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.41,0:22:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! \NDon't park that filthy car in a place like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.60,0:22:10.06,Thought,,0,0,0,,O-Oh crap, there are three of them?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.06,0:22:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't you too cocky \Nfor someone who has to fight alone?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.27,0:22:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Who do you think you're talking to?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.19,0:22:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You prick...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.44,0:22:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.90,0:22:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.46,0:22:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop running and come at me already!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.68,0:22:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.80,0:22:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, friend, do you even know how much this hurts?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:45.65,0:22:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And you just swing it around willy-nilly.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:57.02,0:22:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:59.07,0:23:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Taka-chan...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:04.96,0:23:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo-chan, you're in the fast lane today. {/high pace - whatever that means, probably that he's drinking faster than usual}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:09.39,0:23:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.89,0:23:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You've polished off a whole bottle already.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.67,0:23:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's quite all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.25,0:23:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why are you in uniform?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.07,0:23:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Duh, I'm still on duty, remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.55,0:23:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're working on Sunday?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.14,0:23:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo! There's a bus parked in that alley.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.27,0:23:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,With passengers?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.24,0:23:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. They're probably just killing time too. {himajin = person with a lot of free time on their hands; person of leisure; idler; loafer - probably means "since it's sunday, they're not doing anything important either"}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.58,0:23:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, wanna have some fun on the second floor? {lit: go for a round/quickie}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.53,0:23:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.01,0:23:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.53,0:23:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sober up and get going!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:47.20,0:23:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hopeless, I swear.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:53.62,0:23:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll die. I'll just die! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:55.73,0:23:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll crash into a soapland and die! {maybe it's some slang for getting laid? ; also I trust the viewer to know that soapland is euphemism for prostitution, otherwise might do "massage salon"}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.01,0:24:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is hopeless.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.61,0:24:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! He's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.80,0:24:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Takao-san! You said it was just a little errand, \Nso where've you been for forty minutes?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.31,0:24:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be late getting home!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:12.53,0:24:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.08,0:24:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I'd drop each of you off at your place.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:16.89,0:24:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,After making us wait 40 minutes, that's it? {/only that?}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.58,0:24:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, exactly!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.37,0:24:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine, I'll give you a free ride too.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:29.49,0:24:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, I know. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:31.52,0:24:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I never wanted to be rolling \Nin my bus on a Sunday as well. {korogashi}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:35.28,0:24:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got the reputation of Rolling Ryota to uphold. {????? lit: rolling ryo-san is on the wane (e.g. popularity of something); decline of one's fortunes - probably means "on sunday, I'd want to be rolling in my car/motorcycle, not in the bus, lest everyone forget who I am"}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:46.28,0:24:50.28,Top,,0,0,0,,We could go grab a bite here, right, Yoshimoto-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:50.28,0:24:51.26,Top,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:51.66,0:24:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, if you park your car there, the bus... {will have nowhere to stop}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:58.37,0:25:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You could board your fucking bus from anywhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:03.31,0:25:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh no...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:14.86,0:25:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who's the dumbass \Nthat stopped in a place like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:25.86,0:25:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshimoto-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:27.84,0:25:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn it! He did it, didn't he?!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:31.20,0:25:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:32.51,0:25:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Go ahead, get on!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:36.56,0:25:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! You rammed our car.\NFuck your "Get on!" {\i1}You{\i0} get off, you idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:41.24,0:25:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You telling me to get off?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:44.05,0:25:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:46.21,0:25:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:51.88,0:25:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that attitude?! You're not getting away with just the repair bill, you punk!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:55.74,0:25:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass! {bakayaro}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:57.22,0:25:59.57,Top,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing, Yoshimoto-san?!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:00.38,0:26:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You shut it too! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:02.26,0:26:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so sorry! He doesn't know any better, \Nso please let it slide, yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:08.99,0:26:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, did your bumper get dented?\N If it did, I'll pay for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:14.43,0:26:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. I'll let it slide this once. {lit: good if you understand}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:17.08,0:26:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make sure you never park at a bus stop again.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:21.31,0:26:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. We'll be careful from now on.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:31.95,0:26:33.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,Takao Ryota...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:33.66,0:26:36.39,Thought,,0,0,0,,Can't believe that guy's a bus driver now.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:36.39,0:26:39.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,Guess we'll have to think twice \Nbefore passing any buses from now on.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:41.62,0:26:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:43.60,0:26:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys take care too.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:46.08,0:26:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy for Yoshimoto to say, \Nsince his car didn't get totaled.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:51.07,0:26:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But me? \NMy beloved baby just got rear-ended!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:54.30,0:26:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever did it, \Nwe'll just pay him back in kind!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:58.96,0:27:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! No way we're letting someone \Ntrash our ride and walk away!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:03.10,0:27:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what they call me?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:06.12,0:27:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kattobi Ma-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:07.16,0:27:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:08.04,0:27:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot stuff!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:15.37,0:27:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's roll, Koji!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:16.89,0:27:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:22.89,0:27:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! So you wanna play? {??????????? only hear something about "young"}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:24.98,0:27:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fucker! You smash into our car \Nand just grin about it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:29.06,0:27:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there! \NStop, or I'll make you stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:34.30,0:27:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you on about?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:36.03,0:27:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to ram you in the ass \Nbecause you're a fucking pansy?! {/okama}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:40.10,0:27:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just call me, you boor?! \NOh, now I'm mad!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:43.83,0:27:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:47.12,0:27:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, he dodged them all.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:49.24,0:27:50.63,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Y-You idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:50.63,0:27:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you miss something that big?! \NYou think this is a game?!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:55.07,0:27:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Um, you see...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:57.13,0:28:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You... Y-You jerkface!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:08.63,0:28:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! Nailed the mirror. The mirror.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:12.07,0:28:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Don't get happy over that!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:14.80,0:28:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, fuck, I'm getting dizzy... {probably because the mirror is sideways now}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:18.72,0:28:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't trust you for anything! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:24.87,0:28:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll charge him head-on, bunt-style! {probably the same as in baseball, doesn't seem to have any other meanings}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:28.25,0:28:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's gutsy, Ma-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:34.34,0:28:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamikaze move. \NLet's see if he's got the balls to take it! {lit: suicide tactics}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:41.12,0:28:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:47.04,0:28:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not turning! {????????? just hear something not doing something}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:51.13,0:28:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's out of his mind!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:54.02,0:28:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's looking down on us \Nbecause our car's small!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:57.90,0:29:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he comes again! \NWhen did he catch up?!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:00.76,0:29:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's totally after our asses! {???? no idea what's tsukare here, but it's something he does to their ass - either "destroying [the car's back]" or "tailing it closely", in any case an innuendo is clearly intended, and it seems to mean "he's on our tail"}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:03.04,0:29:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:04.39,0:29:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes the Okama Thrust! {???????? no clue what's that word, bekko?}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:07.91,0:29:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, here he comes! \NToo rough, I hate this.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:11.58,0:29:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Step on it and lose him!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:12.95,0:29:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! I'm flooring it already!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:14.94,0:29:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? {assuming it's koji saying "sou"???}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:15.42,0:29:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?! {??????? no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:16.40,0:29:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's right. That guy's gotta be \Nthe infamous Rolling Ryota.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:21.59,0:29:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:23.14,0:29:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I'm telling you, it's him!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:25.91,0:29:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Koji?!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:27.75,0:29:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:30.60,0:29:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Remembered what?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:32.00,0:29:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If Rolling Ryota's after your ass, \Nyour youth's officially over!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:36.41,0:29:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:38.10,0:29:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no saving us now.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:40.35,0:29:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way to appease that guy \Nis to ditch the car!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:44.26,0:29:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why all the old-timers \Nride bicycles now.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:48.56,0:29:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally couldn't do that. {if I'm hearing it right, he says "my butt can't do it" - probably another joke about how the bicycle seat would thrust into his asshole... explaining lines like this makes me question my life choices}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:50.82,0:29:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:53.08,0:29:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I still got 32 payments left on this car!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:56.63,0:29:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I can afford to ride a bike?! {???? maybe "afford"}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:59.63,0:30:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:11.08,0:30:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Ryota-san, help!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:13.14,0:30:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:14.60,0:30:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Taka-chan got taken by the Panthers gang!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:18.48,0:30:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Panthers?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:19.96,0:30:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They said you have to come \Nto the Arakawa riverbank by seven, or else!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:25.36,0:30:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they want.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:27.28,0:30:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you have to go!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:28.99,0:30:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, they'll dump\N Taka-chan in the river!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:31.86,0:30:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say that, I'm still on duty here.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:34.60,0:30:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go playing the diligent employee now!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:54.54,0:30:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Toshi, what time is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:56.40,0:30:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Way past seven already.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:59.73,0:31:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess even Ryota's lost his nerve, \Nbeing outnumbered like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:03.84,0:31:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid! \NThe boss ain't like you punks! {aniki}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:07.51,0:31:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:10.35,0:31:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe he ditched you already, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:14.40,0:31:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:16.27,0:31:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can join \Nthe trash floating in the river.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:23.22,0:31:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:25.26,0:31:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi! Still at it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:28.30,0:31:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:29.48,0:31:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You showed up, you bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:31.56,0:31:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, knock it off already!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:33.53,0:31:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Another detour?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:34.98,0:31:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A regular ticket won't cover it. \NYou owe us a commuter pass now. {??? idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:39.06,0:31:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, passengers sure talk tough these days.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:43.32,0:31:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel right... {from drinking}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:47.58,0:31:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Not now of all times!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:50.35,0:31:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's drunk! Don't hold back! \NFlatten him, bus and all!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:02.63,0:32:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:05.27,0:32:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:20.61,0:32:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell what's happening anymore. \NAll right, now.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:24.05,0:32:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, whatever. Floor it!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:49.41,0:32:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's my boss! \NEven drunk, he's still got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:55.33,0:32:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! That's enough! You did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:00.94,0:33:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:12.03,0:33:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch, in this state, \NI can't work worth a damn.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:18.41,0:33:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable. I sure have one helluva boss.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:21.33,0:33:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't even tell friend from foe \Nwhen he's hammered.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:22.80,0:33:24.79,Top,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:24.79,0:33:31.53,Top,,0,0,0,,Our talk show tonight welcomes the bus driver \Nwho wiped out an entire biker gang. {wide show = infotainment television program}
Dialogue: 10,0:33:34.25,0:33:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Takao Ryota-san! Welcome!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:41.75,0:33:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Takao, the enemy of biker gangs. \NHow's it going?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:45.76,0:33:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure pulled off something incredible.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:49.08,0:33:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You fought off twenty bikers, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:52.17,0:33:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was desperate, honestly.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:54.17,0:33:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They had me cornered, \Nno way to escape.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:58.20,0:34:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All I could think about was the passengers' safety.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:01.90,0:34:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But with opponents like that, well...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:04.33,0:34:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no choice but to take drastic action.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:07.35,0:34:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you ended up turning \Ntwenty vehicles into scrap metal.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:11.48,0:34:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite a skill you have!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:14.20,0:34:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, driving's my profession, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:16.97,0:34:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a drive together tonight or tomorrow?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:20.08,0:34:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:21.40,0:34:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite a people person, Takao-san. {friendly; openhearted; sociable; amiable; good-humored; good-humoured; frank; candid; willing; ready}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:23.76,0:34:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not really...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:24.67,0:34:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I underestimated you.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:26.72,0:34:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I say? Put a beauty in front of me, \Nand I've got to make a move.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:29.94,0:34:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, no man worth his salt goes\N for the main course before the aperitif. {???????????? no clue what he says or means or what it has to do with the previous line; lit: eating right before the meal man, to his name, what would you say?}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:33.49,0:34:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell's the boss\N getting all the glory?! {lit: became a hero - from the episode title}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:36.68,0:34:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard that biker gangs \Nhave been stirring up a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:41.23,0:34:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Any thoughts on that?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:43.50,0:34:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Drivers should always follow the rules, \Nirrespective of their allegiance. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:47.96,0:34:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Reckless bikers don't deserve \Nto be behind the wheel.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:51.59,0:34:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How dare he...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:53.84,0:34:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Spoken like a true bus driver.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:56.41,0:35:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your professional discipline \Nmade that act of justice possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:01.54,0:35:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you could say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:04.17,0:35:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That fucker! \NWe're not letting this slide!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:08.74,0:35:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll roll again next time! {korogasu}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:15.89,0:00:21.83,Song,,0,0,0,,Someone trusted me with their life {gotta be "Korogashi Ryouta no Uta" by Hidaka Masato; probably goes without saying that no lyrics can be found online, only found one japanese user complaining that even the CD with this song is unobtainium; going by ear}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.30,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll give them mine
Dialogue: 5,0:00:27.30,0:00:30.59,Song,,0,0,0,,In the rear view, the city shines
Dialogue: 5,0:00:30.59,0:00:34.07,Song,,0,0,0,,With the eyes of starving beasts
Dialogue: 5,0:00:34.07,0:00:44.36,Song,,0,0,0,,Ambitious guy, they don't care for your opinion
Dialogue: 5,0:00:44.36,0:00:56.12,Song,,0,0,0,,That's how I roll, roll, roll, roll, Rolling Ryota
Dialogue: 5,0:01:07.09,0:01:12.77,Song,,0,0,0,,If I leave regrets behind and wipe my tears
Dialogue: 5,0:01:12.77,0:01:18.39,Song,,0,0,0,,The woman I loved clings to me
Dialogue: 5,0:01:18.87,0:01:24.11,Song,,0,0,0,,Whether I live for love or die for justice, \NI decide myself
Dialogue: 5,0:01:25.09,0:01:35.40,Song,,0,0,0,,Here I go, proud hands on the wheel
Dialogue: 5,0:01:35.40,0:01:47.88,Song,,0,0,0,,That's how I roll, roll, roll, roll, Rolling Ryota
Dialogue: 5,0:01:57.89,0:02:03.89,Song,,0,0,0,,Blown by the wind, deep in my heart
Dialogue: 5,0:02:03.89,0:02:09.86,Song,,0,0,0,,There's a song for the boys {/my fellow men}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:09.86,0:02:12.69,Song,,0,0,0,,The dawn over Mizutoge burns
Dialogue: 5,0:02:12.69,0:02:16.14,Song,,0,0,0,,Right here inside my chest
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.14,0:02:26.53,Song,,0,0,0,,Fifty thousand horsepower, a man's pride
Dialogue: 5,0:02:26.53,0:02:39.39,Song,,0,0,0,,That's how I roll, roll, roll, roll, Rolling Ryota
Dialogue: 5,0:09:53.16,0:09:58.06,Song,,0,0,0,,His voice {song is 地球の隅で歌をうたおう by 	\N春日章一郎; *sigh* say it with me: going by ear, no lyrics anywhere on the internet}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.63,0:10:05.33,Song,,0,0,0,,Sounds dry now
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.38,0:10:14.96,Song,,0,0,0,,When it came to loving
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.62,0:10:21.81,Song,,0,0,0,,He got lazy
Dialogue: 5,0:10:25.44,0:10:29.92,Song,,0,0,0,,There are seasons
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.49,0:10:38.81,Song,,0,0,0,,But he can't see them
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.37,0:10:48.77,Song,,0,0,0,,Poison runs
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.61,0:10:54.14,Song,,0,0,0,,Through his heart
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.31,0:11:17.93,Song,,0,0,0,,My job
Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.25,0:11:25.42,Song,,0,0,0,,Is to do justice
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.26,0:11:33.61,Song,,0,0,0,,To sing songs
Dialogue: 5,0:11:37.55,0:11:42.14,Song,,0,0,0,,In the far corners of the Earth
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.36,0:11:50.79,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll stay free
Dialogue: 5,0:11:53.20,0:11:58.91,Song,,0,0,0,,Until I die
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.49,0:12:08.77,Song,,0,0,0,,In this corner of the Earth
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.67,0:12:19.47,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll sing my songs
Dialogue: 5,0:35:37.83,0:35:42.35,Song,,0,0,0,,His voice {same song as on 9:53, 地球の隅で歌をうたおう by 	\N春日章一郎, still going by ear}
Dialogue: 5,0:35:45.97,0:35:49.91,Song,,0,0,0,,Sounds dry now
Dialogue: 5,0:35:53.72,0:35:58.89,Song,,0,0,0,,When it came to loving
Dialogue: 5,0:36:01.96,0:36:06.15,Song,,0,0,0,,He got lazy
