Dialogue: 5,0:36:17.83,0:36:22.91,Song,,0,0,0,,But he can't see them
Dialogue: 5,0:36:25.71,0:36:32.92,Song,,0,0,0,,Poison runs
Dialogue: 5,0:36:33.95,0:36:38.61,Song,,0,0,0,,Through his heart
Dialogue: 5,0:36:41.87,0:36:46.37,Song,,0,0,0,,If he could live
Dialogue: 5,0:36:50.21,0:36:53.99,Song,,0,0,0,,Without getting hurt
Dialogue: 5,0:36:57.74,0:37:02.66,Song,,0,0,0,,Life would sure be
Dialogue: 5,0:37:05.89,0:37:09.83,Song,,0,0,0,,An easy gig
Dialogue: 5,0:37:14.02,0:37:17.90,Song,,0,0,0,,But justice
Dialogue: 5,0:37:22.23,0:37:26.81,Song,,0,0,0,,Always comes swinging hard
Dialogue: 5,0:37:29.78,0:37:36.86,Song,,0,0,0,,And the Earth
Dialogue: 5,0:37:38.12,0:37:42.21,Song,,0,0,0,,Must be sick, for sure
